Release 2.1.0 - Xmas16

- Add "Late Addiction" feature to better estimate IBU (fixed PreBoil and recipe flag save)
- Recipe Printing modified to add mash notes plus minur fixes
- Recipe Printing modified to add sparge Volume and acid values 
- Recipe Printing malt late addiction (with mustaches :=) ), malt name wrap text
- Resize Estimated ABV value into recipe window
- Add new feature to export recipe to BeerLAB
- no use cache for target/approximate water
- salt flags are normally unchecked for new recipe
- fix Palmer water calculation for use salt in only mash pot or by splitting in mash and sparge pots
- fix water quantity calculation
- save and use source water from user configuration. It used into new recipes
- Insert attenuation-max attenuation-min temperature-max temperature-min
- Co2 volumes calculation
- Attenuation into yeast table
- Sort tables Malts and Hops
- Improved printing of the recipe
- Configurazione->Impostazioni: move final volume and efficiency into Brewing system data
- Image managment respect from the period of year

